          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781593082833" href="/book/show/911075.Incidents_in_the_Life_of_a_Slave_Girl">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8051792-lisa?shelf=2021-tbr-shelf">2021-tbr-shelf</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8051792-lisa?shelf=classics-19th-century-earlier">classics-19th-century-earlier</a>, 
