        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3797532082" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15192116747820894874">Harriet Jacobs is fiercely determined to be free and to protect her children. Her first person account shows the excruciating trauma that a female slave has to endure - her body owned by an exploitive owner and the constant threat of her children being taken from her. A powerful and important record.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


